title: Okra-and-Corn Maque Choux
directions: Sauté sausage in a large skillet over medium-high heat 3 minutes or until browned. Add onion, bell pepper, and garlic, and sauté 5 minutes or until tender. Add corn, okra, and tomato; cook, stirring often, 10 minutes. Season with salt and pepper to taste.
Note: We tested with Conecuh Original Spicy and Hot Smoked Sausage.
